<div class="title">One Small Snort for Man...</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-7</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=c13h21&Exact=1">c13h21</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; c13h21. "One Small Snort for Man...: An Experience with 2C-T-7 (exp8345)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 26, 2001. erowid.org/exp/8345</div>

<br/>



